> > I follow you except for the vise grips backwards part. can you 
> explain please?

I misspoke.  I should have said "a small pair of _channelocks_", not 
vise-grips.  You insert the head of the channelocks into the hole in 
the middle of the piston and push the handles apart, which grips the 
piston from within.

George Lyle
